 年以下有期徒刑。\r\n\r\n附件：","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c426%2c20220505%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗簡,426,20220505,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"426","JDATE":"20220505","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}